Classes in broad.pda.seq.alignment used by broad.pda.seq.segmentation
StoredAlignmentStats
          Class that manages the storage of an AlignmentDataModelStats to permanent storage Format of the file is simple, the first line stores the timestamp of file creation the next two columns are tab separated lines containing information about the alignment and index file when the stats were stored: Size, last modified date The next line stores the global RPKM constant The next line should be a P if the alignment is paired and anything else, usually U if it is not.
